channel.title: 562 Startup
channel.description:
It appears that when my 562 loading 641 server starts, it does not load npcdrop.cfg. Ingame the only thing NPC's drop is bones. How can I add npcdrop.cfg to the startup?
I have looked through main.java, config.java and configuration.java

item.title: 562 Startup
item.dc:creator: @triger545 triger545
item.description:
@triger545 wrote:

Here. I don’t think this is the problem though.

@echo off
title Robotscape 562
cd src
cd …
“C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre6\bin\java.exe” -Xms250m -Xmx1024m -classpath bin;deps/* com.rs2hd.Main
pause
